query:
SELECT 
  pc.partnershipId,
  pc.childId,
  CONCAT(child.firstName, ' ', child.lastName) as child_name,
  YEAR(child.birthDate) as child_birth_year,
  p.partner1Id,
  p.partner2Id,
  CONCAT(p1.firstName, ' ', p1.lastName) as partner1_name,
  YEAR(p1.birthDate) as partner1_birth_year,
  CONCAT(p2.firstName, ' ', p2.lastName) as partner2_name,
  YEAR(p2.birthDate) as partner2_birth_year
FROM partnership_children pc
JOIN people child ON pc.childId = child.id
JOIN partnerships p ON pc.partnershipId = p.id
JOIN people p1 ON p.partner1Id = p1.id
JOIN people p2 ON p.partner2Id = p2.id
WHERE child.birthDate IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY child.birthDate DESC
LIMIT 10;
